843
00:57:45,051 --> 00:57:47,044
Damn you, Melinda.

844
00:57:47,220 --> 00:57:51,004
If I'm not on guard every moment,
you steal across the border into reality.

845
00:57:51,849 --> 00:57:53,724
There have been thousands
of cases like yours.

846
00:57:53,892 --> 00:57:55,388
And every one, without exception,

847
00:57:55,562 --> 00:57:58,562
has been traced
to something in the person's life.

848
00:57:58,731 --> 00:58:00,309
This life.

849
00:58:02,276 --> 00:58:05,278
Daisy Gamble, somewhere
in some closet of your mind

850
00:58:05,445 --> 00:58:09,193
is the key to all this.
And I intend to find it.

851
00:58:09,366 --> 00:58:14,158
