No, it's the law.

886
01:00:24,582 --> 01:00:27,702
- Haven't you ever been to England?
- Oh, no.

887
01:00:27,877 --> 01:00:30,415
The sea makes me seasick
and I'm afraid of flying.

888
01:00:30,589 --> 01:00:35,416
