I'm afraid of the "no smoking" sign.

889
01:00:35,593 --> 01:00:38,759
- But maybe I can do it now, huh?
- I'm sure.

890
01:00:39,346 --> 01:00:41,386
Wouldn't you like a quick drink?
You have time.

891
01:00:41,557 --> 01:00:43,135
Oh, no, no. Thank you.
I don't think so.

892
01:00:43,309 --> 01:00:45,017
I'm supposed to be
at the Americana at...

893
01:00:45,186 --> 01:00:47,224
- A short one.
