1181
01:20:30,510 --> 01:20:32,135
Where is she now?

1182
01:20:32,638 --> 01:20:36,469
Away with her husband.

1183
01:20:36,641 --> 01:20:40,011
- Are they French too?
- No. No.

1184
01:20:40,186 --> 01:20:42,310
They gave me their apartment
for the summer.

1185
01:20:45,358 --> 01:20:47,731
You sure you're all right?

