01:23:33,105 --> 01:23:34,932
You ought to know.

1226
01:23:35,107 --> 01:23:36,768
Why?

1227
01:23:37,444 --> 01:23:40,278
Do you think I can see
into the future?

1228
01:23:40,779 --> 01:23:42,606
Yes.

1229
01:23:43,574 --> 01:23:46,244
